asset.title: VONZIPPER SUPPORT WILDLIFE TOUR – TRAILER
asset.description: The VonZipper snow team has piled into the yellow van and is headed on the road in search of deep snow, plentiful turns, and creative features. They kicked off the Support Wildlife Tour with a stop at Mammoth Mountain, where John Jackson, Eric Jackson, Brendan Gerard, Gray Thompson, Riley Nickerson, and Josh Naasz took laps through Main Park. Follow the tour... we'll see you on the road #VZWildlifeTour.
asset.author: VonZipper
